Class FacebookEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.facebookjazz.FacebookEvent

  • public class FacebookEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Details of an event retrieved from Facebook.

    Optional Elements

    • description
    • groupPrivacy
    • location

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<event>
  <owner>zjEouhVRISPFGECBCDbUekLaQWObGSsLAyoxhJtyiVVqIDUfumHtvPxIkdvCrgxB</owner>
  <RSVPStatus>NOT_REPLIED</RSVPStatus>
  <location>
    <name>XcDCbTuSKRrZCksoNxfmEDItiGTxBDJrddtDUjxZEddsCPNZSDbpXAFbecSfJrjA</name>
  </location>
  <groupPrivacy>OPEN</groupPrivacy>
  <startTimestamp>1970-03-01T15:01:20+0200</startTimestamp>
  <updatedTimestamp>2005-06-12T22:51:40+0300</updatedTimestamp>
  <description>RZFddVePWxyffgjICtDxlkAzByLnTOusWzLUSdgRFUzKWOlrgZpbKZiXVThPGUgv</description>
  <name>MyxrsIrawdyGjEIEMDGDQhbytXPEFDOknfMgnzUOSrLCcipQaCGZWhrCgqnWgHLc</name>
</event>
